## Critical guards (security-guards.md §5 areas)

Automation never acts unilaterally on:

1. Production data migrations
2. Secret files / keywords
3. Function / worker deploy
4. Payment / billing code
5. Domain-output uncertainty / quality fields

See `hook-config.yml` for the project-specific patterns.

